  <Docs>
    <summary>
            This class specifies the byte encoding for the payload.
            </summary>
    <remarks>
            The encoder is responsible for encoding all of your objects into the correct bytes for the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Azure.Devices.Shared.PayloadConvention" /> that uses it.
            <para>
            By default we have implemented the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Azure.Devices.Shared.Utf8PayloadEncoder" /> class that uses <see cref="P:System.Text.Encoding.UTF8" />
            to handle the encoding for the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Azure.Devices.Shared.DefaultPayloadConvention" /> class.
            </para></remarks>
  </Docs>
